{"title":"(Vue) Mitt 跨元件資料傳遞 Event Bus","uid":"96bb9f6ebbe9a10facda68afdf73a6dd","slug":"Mitt-跨元件資料傳遞（Event-Bus","date":"2021-08-17T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Mitt-跨元件資料傳遞（Event-Bus.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>將兩個完全不同的元件，透過外部套件來實作資料傳遞</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mj8urxt.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"引入-mitt-套件\"><a href=\"#引入-mitt-套件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引入 mitt 套件\"></a>引入 mitt 套件</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsx\" data-language=\"jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x2F;&#x2F; mitt 套件使用起手式\nimport &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;unpkg.com&#x2F;mitt&#x2F;dist&#x2F;mitt.umd.js&#39;; &#x2F;&#x2F; mitt\n&#x2F;&#x2F; const 自訂名稱 &#x3D; mitt 方法\nconst emitter &#x3D; mitt()</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"建立發送資料元件\"><a href=\"#建立發送資料元件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立發送資料元件\"></a>建立發送資料元件</h2><ul>\n<li><p>建立內部資料 product</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>建立內部方法 <code>sendData()</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用 mitt 語法來傳送資料  <code>emitter.emit(&#39;自定義名稱&#39;, 參數)</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>建立元件來觸發方法</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card-body&quot; &gt;\n    &lt;!-- click Event  --&gt;\n    &lt;button @click&#x3D;&quot;sendData&quot;&gt;送出&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;\n  &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<p>完整程式碼：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsx\" data-language=\"jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">const cardEmit &#x3D; &#123;\n    data()&#123;\n      return&#123;\n        product: &#123;\n          name: &#39;蛋餅&#39;,\n          price: 30,\n          vegan: false\n        &#125;,\n      &#125;\n    &#125;,\n    methods:&#123;\n      sendData() &#123;\n        console.log(&#96;sendData 觸發&#96;)\n        &#x2F;&#x2F; 資料往另一個元件做發送\n        &#x2F;&#x2F; emitter.emit(&#39;自定義名稱&#39;,參數)\n        emitter.emit(&#39;sendProduct&#39;, this.product)\n      &#125;\n    &#125;,\n    template:&#96;&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card-body&quot; &gt;\n        &lt;button @click&#x3D;&quot;sendData&quot;&gt;送出&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&#96;\n  &#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"建立監聽＆接收資料元件\"><a href=\"#建立監聽＆接收資料元件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立監聽＆接收資料元件\"></a>建立監聽＆接收資料元件</h2><ul>\n<li>建立接收資料要存放的空間<ul>\n<li><code>item:&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>建立監聽（建議放置在 created 內，確保元件在完成創建時，會被監聽到）</li>\n<li>監聽語法：<code>emitter.on(&#39;自定義名稱&#39;, (參數) ⇒ &#123;...&#125;)</code></li>\n<li>內部元件新增讀取資料方式<ul>\n<li><code>&#123;&#123;item&#125;&#125;</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsx\" data-language=\"jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">const cardOn &#x3D; &#123;\n    data()&#123;\n      return&#123;\n        item:&#123;&#125;\n      &#125;\n    &#125;,\n    created()&#123;\n      &#x2F;&#x2F; 放置在 created 原因為：\n      &#x2F;&#x2F; 當此元件被創建時，就會啟用此 .on 的監聽方法\n      emitter.on(&#39;sendProduct&#39;,(product) &#x3D;&gt; &#123;\n        console.log(&#39;card-on&#39;,product)\n        this.item &#x3D; product\n      &#125;)\n    &#125;,\n    template:&#96;&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card-body&quot;&gt;\n        item: &#123;&#123; item &#125;&#125;\n        &lt;hr&gt;\n        ProductName: &#123;&#123;item.name&#125;&#125;\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&#96;\n  &#125;</code></pre>\n\n<iframe height=\"300\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Mitt 跨元件資料傳遞（Event Bus）\" src=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/embed/NWgPdQN?default-tab=html%2Cresult\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/pen/NWgPdQN\">\n  Mitt 跨元件資料傳遞（Event Bus）</a> by Michael Luo (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo\">@michael-luo</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n","text":"將兩個完全不同的元件，透過外部套件來實作資料傳遞 引入 mitt 套件&#x2F;&#x2F; mitt 套件使用起手式 import &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;unpkg.com&#x2F;mitt&#x2F;dist&#x2F;mitt.umd.js&#3...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-mitt-%E5%A5%97%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">引入 mitt 套件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%99%BC%E9%80%81%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%85%83%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">建立發送資料元件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%9B%A3%E8%81%BD%EF%BC%86%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%85%83%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">建立監聽＆接收資料元件</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Final-Project 需求分析","uid":"dda1dc6fec4e01e6b9f71bae121cafc2","slug":"Final-Project-需求分析","date":"2021-09-27T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Final-Project-需求分析.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"進度 Update5&#x2F;17 週一 補看昨天直播影片 期末專題選題目 租房網站 開始進行需求分析 首頁輪播式照片 (swipper 套件) 因為無會員登入功能，所以將預訂需求改為表單填寫，因此要做”表單驗證”功能 搜尋功能 城市搜尋(ex:台北市) 房型搜尋(ex:四人房...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":45,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"},{"name":"作